  <brief_title>Osteopathy and Obstructive Sleep Apnea Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>a Single Blind Cross Over Trial to Compare Osteopathic Compression of Pterygopalatine Node to Placebo Compression in Obstructive Sleep Apnea Syndrome.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
