  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective is to evaluate an osteopathic compression of pterygopalatine node on sleep
      obstructive apnea syndrome (OSA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Osteopathic compression will be compared to a placebo manoeuvre. Efficacy will be assessed by
      measuring pharyngeal collapsibility
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
